info.author: Doug Hellmann
info.description:
This django application works with django-tagging to apply related
links to other objects.  It is useful, for example, to remember links
related to specific blog posts, hosted projects, etc.  The links are
associated indirectly, via tags.
info.name: django-links
info.summary: Django links application for simple bookmark handling
info.html_description: This django application works with django-tagging to apply related links to other objects. It is useful, for example, to remember links related to specific blog posts, hosted projects, etc. The links are associated indirectly, via tags.
